  </owl:ObjectProperty>
  <owl:Class rdf:about="https://w3id.org/openim/ontology/E-33">
    <rdfs:comment>The structured, versioned multi-year financial plan a wealth manager builds and maintains for a household — the comprehensive advisory artefact the planning review consumes, with the goal hierarchy, the cash-flow model, the retirement and decumulation strategy, the insurance and risk-protection strategy and the estate / wealth-transfer strategy organised into one stored record.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:label>E-33 Financial Plan</rdfs:label>
  </owl:Class>
